description:
Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

A simple APP for working with Latitude Longitude, UTM and MGRS coordinates, Maps and GPS. Register points to be displayed on a map or stored in a database complete with readable address data (geocoding). Capture photo with a watermark containing point name, coordinates and address information. Measure area, distance and registering lines and polygons. Export saved data to CSV or KML file format or locate points in the field using your built-in device's compass and GPS or with generating direction route.

Register Points
UTM Maps allows you to register points and stored in database to display on the map or export to a CSV file. Stored point data will automatically completed with UTM coordinates and readable address (geocoding requires internet access).

Searching for Coordinates
You can search for Latitude, Longitude, UTM, or MGRS coordinates to display on a map or find them in the field using a compass or Direction Route.

Measure Area And Distance
No need to go to the field anymore; now you can measure area and distance with various units using this application. Stores line and polygon data in database and displays it on a map. Export lines and polygons data to KML file.

Data Properties / Point Details
Each data displayed on the map has its own properties, making it easier to navigate and understand. Simply click on a point and the data properties will automatically appear.

Find Point On The Field / Stake Out
Now you can find coordinates or location in the field easily, the application will direct you to the desired coordinate point with the help of the built-in compass on your device or using Direction Route.

Add Photo
Add a photo from camera or library complete with a watermark containing name, coordinates and address information.

Data List & Export
The data list is designed to view data stored in the database, delete unnecessary data, find the location of data in the field or export data to a file. Point data can be exported to CSV files, while line and polygon data can be exported to KML files for use in other software or other devices.

description:
Speedometer GPS: Speed ​​Monitor is a high-precision GPS speedometer that integrates speed monitoring, trip recording, HUD head-up display, speeding reminder and other functions. It provides real-time and accurate speed tracking and navigation assistance for drivers, cyclists, runners and outdoor explorers. Whether it is daily commuting, long-distance travel, or racing competition, this Speedometer app is your ideal choice!

Core functions

Accurate GPS speed measurement

Relying on high-precision GPS technology, it displays the current speed, average speed, and maximum speed in real time to ensure accurate speed measurement. Supports kilometer/hour (km/h) and mile/hour (mph) two unit switching.

Smart speeding alarm

Set a personalized speed limit value. Once the speed is exceeded, the application will issue an alarm to remind you, effectively preventing speeding and helping you drive safely. And it supports 4 preset speed limits, which can be switched with a single click, allowing you to operate more safely while driving!

HUD head-up display mode

After enabling HUD mode, place the phone under the windshield to project the speed information onto the windshield, making night driving safer.

Driving data record

Automatically record detailed data such as travel time, driving distance, stay time, altitude, etc. Allowing you to easily view historical travel data or share it.

Built-in map

The built-in map can display the current location in real time and draw the driving trajectory to prevent getting lost.

Picture-in-Picture Mode (PiP)

Enable Picture-in-Picture (PiP) mode to view speed information in real time while using other applications.
Suitable for scenarios such as navigation and music playback, so that speed measurement no longer affects other operations.
The window size and position can be adjusted to ensure the best visual experience while driving.

Altimeter & Altitude Measurement

Built-in accurate altitude measurement function, real-time monitoring of current altitude, suitable for mountain driving, cycling and outdoor adventures.

Speedometer helps you drive safely, accurately measure speed, and avoid speeding tickets! Download now to experience professional speed measurement service!

Free features:

The following core features are available without a subscription:

Real-time speed measurement

Remaining mileage statistics

Set maximum speed limit

Subscription features (premium features):

Unlock the full feature experience and obtain access through subscription:

Head-up display (HUD) mode

Picture-in-picture (PIP) mode

Map navigation integration

Driving data recording and statistics

Change speed dashboard style

Automatic renewal terms

Subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account. Payment will be charged to the account immediately after confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. The account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and the renewal amount will be determined. Users can manage or cancel subscriptions in "Settings" > "Apple ID" > "Subscriptions". After the free trial (if any) ends, the system will automatically start the subscription according to the selected plan unless canceled in advance.

Our Speedometer app offers a comprehensive solution for monitoring your speed and tracking your journeys, whether you're cycling, driving, boating, or flying. With versatile display options, detailed tracking features, and additional functionalities like music integration and weather updates, this app enhances your travel experience.


● DISPLAY MODE
- Unit Switching: Easily switch between KM/H, MPH, and KTS for speed measurement.
- Analog & Digital Speedometer: Analog speedometer available in portrait mode, and a full-screen digital speedometer in landscape mode.
- Speed Metrics: Display the average and maximum speed of your trip.
- Mode Switching: Switch between bike and car modes, with speed ranges from 120 km/h to 360 km/h.

● SPEED LIMIT ALARM
- Customizable Alerts: Set speed limits and receive notifications when you exceed them.
- Safety Feature: Advanced alerts provide added safety while driving.

● TRACKING
- Journey Tracking: Track traveled distance, average speed, and top speed.
- History Storage: Store tracking data history along with real-time data.
- Tracking Control: Easily turn tracking on or off.
- Time Tracking: Keep track of total travel time.
- Quick Reset: Reset history tracking data quickly and easily.

● CAR CAMERA
- Dash Cam Mode: Use your device as a dash camera to record video during your drive.
- Camera Settings: Customize resolution, orientation, and storage preferences.
- Never lose a moment - securely upload and store your dashcam recordings in the cloud, managing and accessing your trips anytime, anywhere.

● PARKING
- Park/Unpark: Mark your parked vehicle and unpark when ready to leave.
- Map Support: Works seamlessly across all map views – Standard, Satellite, and Hybrid.
- Navigation to Vehicle: Navigate back to your parked location using Google Maps, Apple Maps, or built-in in-app navigation. Displays     real-time distance between you and your parked car.

● MAP
- Live Tracking: Display current speed and distance on the map.
- Real-Time Positioning: Show your current position on the map with Standard, Satellite, or Hybrid view options.

● WEATHER
- Current Conditions: Display weather conditions for your current location.
- Sunrise & Sunset: Show sunrise and sunset times.

● GPS INDICATOR
- Accuracy Indicator: Shows the accuracy of your GPS signal.

● WATCH SUPPORT
- Full Tracking Control: Start, pause, and stop trip tracking directly from your Apple Watch.
- Live Map View: See your live trip tracking map right on your watch screen.
- Easy Monitoring: Check speed, distance, and time without touching your phone.
- Saved Trips Sync: All saved trips on your watch can be viewed anytime on the connected iPhone.
- Seamless Experience: Use the app from your wrist while riding, walking, or driving.

● DRIVING PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS & SCORE 
- Track how well you drive with detailed analysis of your speed, braking, and acceleration. Get a driving score after each trip to improve safety and efficiency.
 
● NOTE:
- Battery Usage: Continued use of GPS in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
- GPS Accuracy: GPS accuracy may vary due to device hardware sensor limitations.
- Data Connection: A data connection is required to view the map.
- Location Services: Ensure location services are enabled for the application. Go to Settings > Privacy > Location Services > ON.
- Enhance your travel experience with our all-in-one Speedometer app, designed for convenience and safety.

Using Coordinator app, you can collect coordinate data from land on whatever coordinate system you want, choosing from defined systems. You can collect GPS coordinates. You can use the app as a GPS tracker. You can view a coordinate data on the map. You can search by longitude/latitude. You can convert an existing coordinate into another coordinate system. You can display circumference and area measurements of some coordinates by opening the file which created before. Also you can measure distance and area for some coordinates which determined manually on the map. You can display a KML file on the map. Coordinator app contains several useful tools for people interested in coordinates, maps and geographic information systems (GIS).
Coordinator offers Cloud Database Functions (creating points, lines & polygons, sharing your layers with teammates, working simultaneously with teammates, working offline and synchronizing, etc), exporting to KML & Excel files, get elevation value of points and so on. You can create your layers and share that layers with your teammates. You can instantaneously see the data which is created by other friends on the map instantaneously.
Besides longitude/latitude, subscribers can find out the altitude value of a point on the map. Subscribers can use the Coordinator Web app. So that you can use the cloud database features of the Coordinator app on the web page on your computer and monitor the data instantly. You can view/track and edit cloud database data on the web page. In this way, you can instantly monitor the data movements made in the mobile app in the field, in the web browser on your computer.

You can use Speed Camera Radar to detect hazards on the road, such as speed cameras, red-light cameras, speed bumps, bad roads, etc.
The application uses a database of points filled with love by other users.

Find your country or region from the list, and you're good to go! You will see all the alerts on the map.
Turn on the detection, and the application will warn you when something on the way is about to spoil your day.
Not interested in some types of hazards? Filter them out on the preferences page.
Contribute! Rate down the hazard if you hadn't seen it or thumbs up if it's on the place. We will remove threats with low ratings as invalid.
Add you're highly welcome to add your own points if they are not in the database.

Be careful on the road and good luck!

The workflow of the application differs from the hardware radar detector. Hardware radar detector - is a passive receiver that does not block the signal to which it is set, but simply notify the driver of the presence in the field of the radar radio interference.
This application works differently: it uses a database of hazards previously detected by other users.

Mapway - Your Ultimate Public Transport Companion!  

 
Navigate the world's busiest cities with ease using Mapway, the go-to transit app designed for tourists, travellers and commuters like you. Seamlessly blending transit and geographic maps, Mapway provides a comprehensive view of metro, subway, and tram networks across major cities worldwide. 

 

Key Features: 

 
1. Instantly Change City: Easily switch between cities within the app to plan routes and explore transit networks in different locations seamlessly whether traveling for work or for pleasure. 

2. Amazing Interactive Maps: Schematic maps redesigned from the ground up specifically for mobile devices, full of interactive features to provide you with clear city navigation. 

3. Simple Journey Planning: Straightforward journey planning with clear step-by-step guidance and live information making navigating cities simple. 

4. No Signal, No Problem: Plan routes between stations even without an internet connection, perfect for navigating underground or roaming abroad. 

5. Live City Updates: Stay informed with real-time transit information and station status for select cities. Never miss a train or tram again with up-to-the-minute alerts. 

6. Live Departure Boards: Real-time departure information to ensure you never miss your train, tram or bus. 

7. Crowdsourced Station Busyness: Make informed decisions on your routes with live information from fellow commuters & travellers. Join the community helping each other. 

8. Save Favourite Stations: Save your favourite stations for quick access and personalized navigation. 

9. Live Map Updates: You will always have the latest transit map in your pocket with our live over-the-air map updates.
